snippet: FROM PERNAMBUCO.--We have advices from Pernambuco to the 30th August. The news is not important, but intelligence was anxiously awaited from the River Plate. The steamer El Moro was fully due, at the date of our last advices....
lead_paragraph: FROM PERNAMBUCO.--We have advices from Pernambuco to the 30th August. The news is not important, but intelligence was anxiously awaited from the River Plate. The steamer El Moro was fully due, at the date of our last advices.
